characters and show off your swag!<br>-A poseable photo mode to let you show off your creativity!<br>-True Co-Op; play with your best friend and cooperate or race together towards the end of each level!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312160/extras/a065684f8177fca72c3501e7aedb1ee8.poster.avif?t=1726175409\" width=448 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312160/extras/a065684f8177fca72c3501e7aedb1ee8.webm?t=1726175409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312160/extras/a065684f8177fca72c3501e7aedb1ee8.mp4?t=1726175409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
